;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fsocial%2Ffood_1.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-cap-ink/90 via-cap-ink/40 to-transparent \n                md:bg-gradient-to-l md:from-cap-ink/90 md:via-cap-ink/50 md:to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-6 font-sans text-xs font-medium tracking-widest text-white/70 \n                left-6 md:left-12\">PHOTO © <!-- -->Cap Congo Agricole Bandundu, Mushie Pentane</div></div></div><div class=\"relative z-10 -mt-[100vh] w-full\"><div class=\"flex min-h-screen w-full items-end px-6 pb-24 md:items-center md:px-16 lg:px-24 \n              justify-start md:justify-start\"><div class=\"w-full max-w-2xl text-left\"><div class=\"mb-8 h-1 w-16 bg-cap-yellow \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"></div><h2 class=\"font-unbounded text-4xl font-bold uppercase leading-tight tracking-wide text-white drop-shadow-lg md:text-5xl lg:text-7xl\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\">Hôpital de Babama</h2><p class=\"mt-6 max-w-xl text-lg font-light leading-relaxed text-white/90 drop-shadow md:mt-8 md:text-2xl \n                  \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\">Dans le cadre de ses actions communautaires à Babama, la société Cap Congo Agro Palm a procédé à la construction d&#x27;un hôpital afin d&#x27;améliorer l&#x27;accès aux soins de santé pour la population locale.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex min-h-screen w-full items-end px-6 pb-24 md:items-center md:px-16 lg:px-24 \n              justify-start md:justify-end\"><div class=\"w-full max-w-2xl text-left md:text-right\"><div class=\"mb-8 h-1 w-16 bg-cap-yellow md:ml-auto\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"></div><h2 class=\"font-unbounded text-4xl font-bold uppercase leading-tight tracking-wide text-white drop-shadow-lg md:text-5xl lg:text-7xl\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\">CS Babama</h2><p class=\"mt-6 max-w-xl text-lg font-light leading-relaxed text-white/90 drop-shadow md:mt-8 md:text-2xl \n                  md:ml-auto\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\">Le chantier du CS Babama a accueilli la visite du Bourgmestre de Lubunga, un encouragement fort pour notre engagement social.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex min-h-screen w-full items-end px-6 pb-24 md:items-center md:px-16 lg:px-24 \n              justify-start md:justify-start\"><div class=\"w-full max-w-2xl text-left\"><div class=\"mb-8 h-1 w-16 bg-cap-yellow \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"></div><h2 class=\"font-unbounded text-4xl font-bold uppercase leading-tight tracking-wide text-white drop-shadow-lg md:text-5xl lg:text-7xl\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\">Don de vareuses</h2><p class=\"mt-6 max-w-xl text-lg font-light leading-relaxed text-white/90 drop-shadow md:mt-8 md:text-2xl \n                  \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\">La société Cap Congo Agro Palm a procédé à un don de vareuses en faveur de la population de Lubunga, témoignant ainsi de son engagement social et de sa proximité avec les communautés locales.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex min-h-screen w-full items-end px-6 pb-24 md:items-center md:px-16 lg:px-24 \n              justify-start md:justify-end\"><div class=\"w-full max-w-2xl text-left md:text-right\"><div class=\"mb-8 h-1 w-16 bg-cap-yellow md:ml-auto\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"></div><h2 class=\"font-unbounded text-4xl font-bold uppercase leading-tight tracking-wide text-white drop-shadow-lg md:text-5xl lg:text-7xl\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\">Distribution de maïs</h2><p class=\"mt-6 max-w-xl text-lg font-light leading-relaxed text-white/90 drop-shadow md:mt-8 md:text-2xl \n                  md:ml-auto\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\">Dans le cadre de ses actions communautaires, la Société Cap Congo agricole Bandundu avait organisé une distribution de maïs en faveur de la communauté de Mushie Pentane, contribuant ainsi au soutien alimentaire et au développement des communautés locales.</p></div></div></div></section></main><!--$--><!--/$--><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/1vd3biehm0nus.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[31172,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/07j_tx7hiq-y2.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/2f0xpn84novj6.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/19whmydmhik_0.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"LenisRoot\\\"]\\n3:I[39075,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/07j_tx7hiq-y2.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/2f0xpn84novj6.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/19whmydmhik_0.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n4:I[39756,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/07j_tx7hiq-y2.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/2f0xpn84novj6.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/19whmydmhik_0.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n5:I[37457,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/07j_tx7hiq-y2.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/2f0xpn84novj6.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/19whmydmhik_0.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n6:I[47257,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/07j_tx7hiq-y2.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/2f0xpn84novj6.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/19whmydmhik_0.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"ClientPageRoot\\\"]\\n7:I[52297,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/07j_tx7hiq-y2.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/2f0xpn84novj6.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/19whmydmhik_0.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/13oqczmuidks4.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/31e3g8_zbep3k.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\na:I[97367,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/07j_tx7hiq-y2.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/2f0xpn84novj6.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/19whmydmhik_0.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"OutletBoundary\\\"]\\nb:\\\"$Sreact.suspense\\\"\\ne:I[97367